 15  -- There is an awkward difficulty with universes here.
 16  -- If we allowed `J` to be a small category in `Prop`, we'd run into trouble
 17  -- because `yoneda.obj (F : (J โฅค C)แตแต)` will be a functor into `Sort (max v 1)`,
 18  -- not into `Sort v`.
 19  -- So we don't allow this case; it's not particularly useful anyway.
